Sentencas: Niobium-doped strontium titanate was used as the anode for a solid oxide fuel cell.
Titulo: Solid oxide fuel cells with Ni-infiltrated perovskite anode

Sentencas: Electrolyte-supported cells were prepared with pure perovskite and composite perovskite-yttria-stabilized-zirconia (YSZ) anodes.
Titulo: Solid oxide fuel cells with Ni-infiltrated perovskite anode

Sentencas: Fuel cell tests demonstrated significant improvement in power density after infiltration with a small amount of Ni.
Titulo: Solid oxide fuel cells with Ni-infiltrated perovskite anode

Sentencas: The obtained values of power densities are comparable with conventional Ni/YSZ cermet anode.
Titulo: Solid oxide fuel cells with Ni-infiltrated perovskite anode

Sentencas: In addition, stability tests showed initial degradation followed by stable operation.
Titulo: Solid oxide fuel cells with Ni-infiltrated perovskite anode
